extendedInfo.description: Touch the screen and you make some angry birds which make them fly away. Wait a little bit and they will come back. Choose between 7 different background colours and the colour of the tree and birds. The latest live wallpaper from DictatorDesigns.

reviews.title: Gorgeous!
reviews.comment: Simple and one of my favorites in LWP! Graphics are great and animation is not overwhelming but gentle. Hope there\'s more to come but plenty of options at this point.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Doing something wrong?
reviews.comment: My doesn\'t do anything? Galaxy tab. The birds dont move and I\'m confused as to what this is suppose to be, a screen saver?
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Laggy, unresponsive, would not even show up! I opened it, and it did not show the lwp at all. Just a black screen. Otherwise, fine.
